Messages.Value: Good morning, thank you for calling XYZ travel agency, my name is Zoe, how can I assist you today?
Hi Zoe, my name is John Smith and I need some assistance with my travel plans.
Of course John, how can I assist you with that?
I recently traveled from New York City to Los Angeles and my luggage got lost during the flight.
I'm really sorry to hear that John. Can you please provide me with your flight details and your baggage claim number so I can track down your luggage and help you reclaim it?
Sure, my flight was with American Airlines, flight AA1234, departing from JFK airport in New York City on February 20th at 2pm. My baggage claim number is AA5678.
Thank you for the details John, let me check with American Airlines and see what the status of your luggage is. Please hold on for a moment.
Thank you for holding John, I was able to track down your luggage and it is currently on its way to Los Angeles. You should be able to reclaim it at LAX airport in a couple of hours.
That's great news Zoe, thank you very much for your help!
